---
/* BetaCTA â€” Replaces placeholder testimonials with community call-to-action */
---

<section id="community" class="py-24 md:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
    <!-- Headline -->
    <h2 class="font-headline font-semibold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-text-primary text-balance text-center mb-6 fade-in-up">
      Help us build the best voice-to-text tool.
    </h2>

    <p class="font-body text-text-secondary text-lg text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 fade-in-up">
      QuickSay is in beta. We're looking for real users to test it, break it, and tell us what to build next. Join the beta and get a free lifetime license.
    </p>

    <!-- Two-card layout -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 fade-in-up">
      <!-- Card 1: Join Beta -->
      <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 9v3m0 0v3m0-3h3m-3 0h-3m-2-5a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM3 20a6 6 0 0112 0v1H3v-1z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-headline font-semibold text-xl text-text-primary">Join the Beta</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-text-secondary text-[15px] leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">
          Get free lifetime access to QuickSay. Test it with your workflow, in your apps, on your machine. All we ask is honest feedback.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/beta"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-accent-teal text-background font-headline font-semibold rounded-lg px-6 py-3 min-h-[44px] hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-teal-glow active:scale-[0.98] transition-all duration-150"
          data-analytics="beta-cta-homepage"
        >
          Get Beta Access
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Share Feedback -->
      <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent-orange/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-orange" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.5 8.25h9m-9 3H12m-9.75 1.51c0 1.6 1.123 2.994 2.707 3.227 1.129.166 2.27.293 3.423.379.35.026.67.21.865.501L12 21l2.755-4.133a1.14 1.14 0 01.865-.501 48.172 48.172 0 003.423-.379c1.584-.233 2.707-1.626 2.707-3.228V6.741c0-1.602-1.123-2.995-2.707-3.228A48.394 48.394 0 0012 3c-2.392 0-4.744.175-7.043.513C3.373 3.746 2.25 5.14 2.25 6.741v6.018z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-headline font-semibold text-xl text-text-primary">Share Feedback</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-text-secondary text-[15px] leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">
          Already a beta tester? Tell us what's working, what's not, and what you want next. Every response shapes the product.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/beta/feedback"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.15)] text-text-primary font-headline font-semibold rounded-lg px-6 py-3 min-h-[44px] hover:bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.05)] active:scale-[0.98] transition-all duration-150"
          data-analytics="feedback-cta-homepage"
        >
          Give Feedback
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
